{"tid":1393232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"總會有完既一日？你決定唔到既嘢就等我決定。","createTime":"2019-08-01T04:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:06:15.000Z","uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1d3c5d78eab7d42d51d7dc67bf93f4280ef366b","tid":1393232,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"純粹叫春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n身為第三者既我，就算我幾愛佢都好，<br />\n就算呢一刻佢有幾在乎我。都會有完既一日吧？<br />\n開開心心過埋月底呢個生日就算啦好嗎？<br />\n我好清楚你唔會放棄佢，而我亦係一個好自私既人。<br />\n我想要獨佔你，既然唔能夠同你名正言順一齊到最後，<br />\n我寧願放手。呢段甜蜜溫馨既時光，成為回憶比較好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預祝我們生日快樂🎂"},{"pid":"7e1948ded245c8192071c8f5e2bc905ae2b66184","tid":1393232,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"好可憐 自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d43cc5ab00cb15b4264a3ccc902ad21db55f483","tid":1393232,"uid":215200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"狗公"},{"pid":"394f04e19e0e447e6dcd7a986c22d8d9bf153cea","tid":1393232,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d43cc5ab00cb15b4264a3ccc902ad21db55f483","tid":1393232,"uid":215200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:07:41.000Z","msg":"狗公"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T05:09:55.000Z","msg":"受騙的那個比騙徒更混帳<br />\n你估吓我係邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87075aff80b7c10794a0c58e57bef489a7c2b099","tid":1393232,"uid":118945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7befc199742acb615a9de13a1a817970aeded907","tid":1393232,"uid":271339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"